PLUGINS:
✅ [OT Local Runtime Config] Applies local runtime-only config normalization without changing tracked Open Ticket files.
✅ [OT-Dashboard] A configurable web dashboard for Open Ticket.
✅ [Welcome Message by Eseclick] Simple welcome embed plugin for Open Ticket
✅ [OT Alt Detector] Use the discord-alt-detector npm package in your ticket bot!
✅ [OT Channel Display] A plugin to show different variables in a voice channel in your server.
✅ [OT Config Reload] Adds a config reload command.
✅ [OT EoTFS Bridge] Local-only whitelist intake bridge for EoTFS Open Ticket.
✅ [OT Feedback] A plugin to gather feedback of your support service!
✅ [OT Follow-Ups] Send additional follow-up messages to a ticket.
✅ [OT HTML Transcripts] Local HTML transcript archive, renderer, and public host for Open Ticket.
✅ [OT Restrictions] Restrict which roles can open a specific ticket option.
✅ [OT Reviews] Review system for Open Ticket! It is very customisable and has lots of features.
✅ [OT SQLite Database] With this plugin, the database will be an SQLite file! It's a must-have for large servers!
✅ [OT Tags] Use tags to quickly reply with a pre-existing text!
✅ [OT Template System] Predefined template system for sending quick messages.
✅ [OT Ticket Forms] An advanced forms plugin for Open Ticket.
✅ [OT Volume Warning] Alerts ticket creators when too many tickets are open, indicating possible response delays.
💤 [Example Plugin] A simple template for an Open Ticket v4 plugin!
💤 [OT Assign Role] Automatically assigns a role to ticket creators.

